,('quantitative', 'Shape A: a circle with radius 4. Shape B: a square with side 7. Which has the greater area? (Use π ≈ 3.14)', NULL, '["A is greater", "B is greater", "Equal", "Cannot determine"]'::jsonb, 0, 2, 'A: 3.14 × 4² = 3.14 × 16 ≈ 50.2. B: 7² = 49. A is greater by a small margin.')
